KitKat::

She looked at Blackfang and wondered how in the matrix another wolf 
had come to the planet without her knowledge. She followed him and 
wondered how his leader would take a predacon walking the halls in 
his base. She wondered how long untill they either killed her or 
tried to take her down. 

Camoflage::
She skipped behind them and was grinning ear to ear. Her little form 
hopping around and showing all sorts of glee.
